    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154870/extras/a884f3b51c130468b28b0c4bd0db8f7d.avif?t=1725543964\" width=642 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diving into a Forgotten Past</h2>In the game &quot;RAYS,&quot; you take on the role of Adam, a character who wakes up in a hospital with no memory of his past. Completely alone, he is forced to embark on a challenging journey filled with numerous trials and unexpected events. Every step he takes is accompanied by <strong>intense and emotional moments</strong> that stay with the player long after.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154870/extras/ce5e2b28159f1e4b407a644d86bc6590.poster.avif?t=1725543964\" width=400 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154870/extras/ce5e2b28159f1e4b407a644d86bc6590.webm?t=1725543964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your Choices, Your Fate</h2>The game offers <strong>over five different endings</strong>, each dependent on your choices and interactions with the world. Throughout the game, you will uncover the personalities of <strong>more than 15 characters</strong>, each of whom can influence how your story concludes. Thanks to innovative mechanics such as the <strong>map</strong> and <strong>hints</strong>, you will gain a better understanding of how to achieve the best outcomes and uncover all the game's secrets.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154870/extras/cc256d70dfa28212f57480a6296cbb8c.avif?t=1725543964\" width=200 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Visual and Auditory Excellence</h2>Visually, &quot;RAYS&quot; impresses with its variety: <strong>over 100 unique backgrounds</strong> and carefully crafted <strong>ambient music</strong> accompany you throughout the game, creating an immersive atmosphere. Environmental sounds — such as footsteps, the creak of a door, or the clink of a sword — bring the game world to life, immersing the player in every character's action, <strong>enhancing the sense of presence</strong> and realism.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154870/extras/468de876e5787d26cc33e71a79792ecb.avif?t=1725543964\" width=200 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Total Immersion in the World</h2>A complete immersion into a world where <strong>every decision matters</strong>. Diverse story branches and well-developed characters create a <strong>unique experience</strong> that makes you ponder every detail.",
